title: [Annex, White Haven Lobby]
description: Simple, but elegant, the teakwood flooring of this room is polished to a lustrous sheen.  A white velvet pennant edged with icy blue hangs between a heavy, white muslin curtain and an embroidered blue muslin curtain.
